[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man and woman charged over Galashiels 'attempted murder'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man and woman have been charged in connection with an attempted murder in the Borders.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident took place around 01:30 on Saturday at a flat on Torwoodlee Road, Galashiels.
A 30-year-old man suffered serious injuries and was taken to Borders General Hospital.
A 31-year-old woman and a 23-year-old man are expected to appear at Jedburgh Sheriff Court on Monday.
